text: Justice Prashant Mishra (born 29 August 1964) is an Indian judge. Presently, he is a judge on the Chhattisgarh High Court. He has served as the Acting Chief Justice of the Chhattisgarh High Court.Devika,& TRANSFER NEWS.html "Chhatisgarh HC : Justice Prashant Kumar Mishra appointed as Chief Justice", The SCC Online Blog, 23 March 2019 ==See also== *List of current Indian chief justices *List of Chief Justices of India ==References== Category:Chief Justices of India Category:Living people Category:1964 births
title: Prashant Kumar Mishra
